OL,3,CUniversity contributed to death of
OL,4,Cstudent who took her own life, court
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe High Court has found the
OL,8,FUniversity of Bristol contributed to
OL,9,Fthe death of a student who took her
OL,10,Fown life while suffering from a mental
OL,11,Fhealth condition.
OL,13,FNatasha Abrahart, originally from
OL,14,FNottinghamshire, was in her second
OL,15,Fyear of an undergraduate physics
OL,16,Fdegree at the University of Bristol
OL,17,Fwhen on the day she was due to give a
OL,18,Fpresentation.
