OL,3,CUniversity contributed to death of
OL,4,Cstudent who took her own life, court
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FOn 14 February the judge rejected the
OL,8,FUniversity's appeal against an earlier
OL,9,Fjudgment that found it had contributed
OL,10,Fto her death by discriminating against
OL,11,Fher.
OL,13,FMr Justice Linden dismissed the
OL,14,FUniversity's case and found that the
OL,15,FUniversity had failed on all seven of
OL,16,Fits grounds of appeal.
