OL,3,CUniversity contributed to death of
OL,4,Cstudent who took her own life, court
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe High Court heard how 20-year-old
OL,8,FNatasha had social anxiety that
OL,9,Famounted to a disability and was "very
OL,10,Fmuch under pressure" to attend oral
OL,11,Fassessments.
OL,13,FAfter the hearing, Natasha's parents,
OL,14,FRobert and Margaret Abrahart, read a
OL,15,Fstatement.
OL,17,FRobert Abrahart, a retired university
OL,18,Flecturer, said: "It has been a long
OL,19,Fand painful journey to reach this
OL,20,Fpoint, and the University of Bristol
OL,21,Fhas fought us every step of the way.
