OL,3,CUniversity contributed to death of
OL,4,Cstudent who took her own life, court
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"The result is that we now have a
OL,8,Fjudgment from the High Court
OL,9,Fconfirming what we always knew to be
OL,10,Ftrue.
OL,12,F"The University of Bristol failed our
OL,13,Fdaughter, broke the law, and
OL,14,Fcontributed to her death.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/14
