OL,3,CUniversity contributed to death of
OL,4,Cstudent who took her own life, court
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FMargaret Abrahart, a retired
OL,8,Fpsychological wellbeing practitioner,
OL,9,Fsaid: "We have been able to get some
OL,10,Fmeasure of justice for Natasha because
OL,11,Fshe was disabled and therefore covered
OL,12,Fby the Equality Act.
OL,14,F"But what about students who aren't
OL,15,Fdisabled? They need a statutory duty
OL,16,Fof care.
