OL,3,CUniversity contributed to death of
OL,4,Cstudent who took her own life, court
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"128,000 people signed a petition
OL,8,Fcalling for a statutory duty requiring
OL,9,Funiversities to act with reasonable
OL,10,Fcare and skill to avoid harming
OL,11,Fstudents, but the Government kicked
OL,12,Fthe issue into the long grass.
OL,14,F"Do Keir Starmer, Rishi Sunak, and the
OL,15,Fother party leaders really think
OL,16,Funiversities should be allowed to
OL,17,Fcause harm to their students by acting
OL,18,Fwithout reasonable care and skill? If
OL,19,Fthey don't, then they should prove it.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/14
