OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F438A1707984725
OL,3,CUniversity contributed to death of
OL,4,Cstudent who took her own life, court
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Put a statutory duty of care for
OL,8,Funiversities in your manifestos, or
OL,9,Fexplain to the voters why you think
OL,10,Fthat some students should be protected
OL,11,Fwhile others are not."
OL,13,FBoth parents have campaigned for
OL,14,Funiversities to have a duty of care
OL,15,Fover their students.
OL,17,FLast year, they visited No.10 Downing
OL,18,FStreet to hand over a petition signed
OL,19,Fby nearly 130,000 people.
