OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe campaign refers to the "100
OL,8,Fstudents who take their own lives
OL,9,Fevery year" and calls on the
OL,10,Fgovernment to make universities
OL,11,Fresponsible for their students'
OL,12,Fwelfare.
OL,14,FFollowing the High Court's ruling, the
OL,15,FUniversity of Bristol has issued a
OL,16,Fresponse.
