OL,3,CUniversity contributed to death of
OL,4,Cstudent who took her own life, court
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FProfessor Evelyn Welch, Vice-
OL,8,FChancellor and President of the
OL,9,FUniversity of Bristol, said:
OL,10,F"Natasha's death is a tragedy - I am
OL,11,Fdeeply sorry for the Abrahart family's
OL,12,Floss.
OL,14,F"At Bristol, we care profoundly for
OL,15,Fall our students and their mental
OL,16,Fhealth and wellbeing is a priority and
OL,17,Fis at the heart of everything we do.
OL,18,FWe continue to develop and improve our
OL,19,Fservices and safeguards to support our
OL,20,Fstudents who need help.
