OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Higher Education staff across the
OL,8,Fcountry share our deep concern about
OL,9,Fthe increase of mental health issues
OL,10,Famongst young people, and with that
OL,11,Frise comes the increasing importance
OL,12,Fthat staff, students, and their
OL,13,Ffamilies are clear on what support
OL,14,Funiversities can and should provide,
OL,15,Fand that students receive appropriate
OL,16,Fspecialist care under the NHS should
OL,17,Fthey need it.
