OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"In 2022 Bristol became one of the
OL,8,Ffirst universities to receive the
OL,9,FUniversity Mental Health Charter
OL,10,FAward, which recognises the continued
OL,11,Fhard work of our staff and students in
OL,12,Fterms of taking a strong, structured
OL,13,Fapproach towards improving mental
OL,14,Fhealth and wellbeing across our
OL,15,Funiversity. We know there is always
OL,16,Fmore to do, and we will keep working
OL,17,Fto achieve the best for everyone in
OL,18,Four community."
